descript.abstract: Public view of the parcel layer. This view is limited to only the attributes that can be seen by the general public.This Parcel layer was compiled from a number of sources. Digital data was provided by each of the local cities. These files were projected to State Plane coordinate system and combined together. The remaining areas were created from the Assessor's map books. Each page was scanned and then projected to real world coordinates then rubber sheeting was used to fit all the pieces together. The final product varies in accuracy based on location. Urban areas are relatively accurate while more rural areas are less accurate. In some cases, the parcels can be significantly off from their true location

dataIdInfo.idAbs:
Public view of the parcel layer. This view is limited to only the attributes that can be seen by the general public.

This Parcel layer was compiled from a number of sources. Digital data was provided by each of the local cities. These files were projected to State Plane coordinate system and combined together. The remaining areas were created from the Assessor's map books. Each page was scanned and then projected to real world coordinates then rubber sheeting was used to fit all the pieces together. The final product varies in accuracy based on location. Urban areas are relatively accurate while more rural areas are less accurate. In some cases, the parcels can be significantly off from their true location
